snippet.title: Baloo & The Big Blue - The Epic Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a trailer for my game for the Playdate console.  It is free on itchio and the link is below.  This is my second game as an Indie game developer.  Help with the video and editing was done by Ms. IrishJiminy.  If you like the game please share it, leave a comment here or on itchio and tell your friends!

https://irishjiminy.itch.io/baloo-and-the-big-blue
